data.description: This 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condominium is conveniently located near popular attractions such as Six Flags Over Texas, Globe Life Field, and AT&T Stadium. Situated on the second floor, this unit offers a desirable level of privacy and a great view. One notable feature of this condo is the added washer dryer utility area. Unlike other units in the complex that rely on the on-site laundromat, this unit provides the convenience and comfort of having your own in-unit laundry facility. The beautiful condo and been completely redone in the last 2 years including new appliances, AC, paint, flooring, and tiles and counters through out. The condo itself boasts a well-designed layout, with two spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. This setup ensures that residents have plenty of space and privacy. The location of this condo is a major advantage. Whether you're a sports enthusiast or enjoy thrilling rides, this neighborhood offers a range of activities to suit all tastes.
